				\begin{document}$$RMSD = \sqrt {\frac{1}{N}\mathop \sum \limits_{i = 1}^{N} d_{i}^{2} }$$\end{document}where N is the number of atoms in the ligand, and di is the Euclidean distance between the ith pair of corresponding atoms.
